files.name: google
files.content:
<Button
        className="outline outline-2 w-full flex gap-5 outline-gray-700"
        variant="ghost"
        size="lg"
        onClick={() => handleOauth("google")}
      >
        <Image
          src="https://utfs.io/f/eb04033a-a0af-402c-b691-1ffeadec8c91-c3fgyx.svg"
          alt="google"
          width={20}
          height={20}
          className="w-6 h-6"
        />
        Continue with Google
      </Button>

files.name: github
files.content:
<Button
        className="outline outline-2 w-full flex gap-5 outline-gray-700 group"
        variant="ghost"
        size="lg"
        onClick={() => handleOauth("github")}
      >
        <Image
          src="https://utfs.io/f/d3274ee5-df7a-467b-a974-6b4197ee1aa5-n8iwbn.svg"
          alt="github"
          width={20}
          height={20}
          className="w-6 h-6 invert group-hover:invert-0"
        />
        Continue with Github
      </Button>
